    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一大群可爱灵正蜂拥而至……他们只想要拥抱！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在他们靠近之前，朝他们的脸开枪，否则你将被纯粹、无情的可爱淹没！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294950/extras/aef8d85c6ac1bc945c2f132c6097fd3c.poster.avif?t=1771508633\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294950/extras/aef8d85c6ac1bc945c2f132c6097fd3c.webm?t=1771508633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294950/extras/aef8d85c6ac1bc945c2f132c6097fd3c.mp4?t=1771508633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为反派！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在随机生成的地图上生存下来，体验30到90秒的快速Roguelite回合，每张地图都有独特的危险——沼泽、陷阱、毒河、极寒等着你！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>选择你的战士！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24位独特角色，每位都有专属武器、属性和特殊技能。每一局都是全新的体验！挑战不同难度，解锁所有角色！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>死亡、升级、再来！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >死亡只是变强的一步！升级你的武器，投资技能树，变得更强大，回来屠杀更多可爱的小东西！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
